condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section A.1 (a) | Description :The Borrower shall: (a) ensure overall Projectcoordination through the CCU; and | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section A.1 (b) | Description :(b) maintain the CCU with functions andresponsibilities satisfactory to the Bank and with staff in adequate numbers whose qualifications and experience are at all timessatisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section A.2 | Description :The Borrower shall implement the Project in accordancewith the provisions of the POPM and shall not amend, suspend, abrogate, repeal or waive any provision of the POPM without priorapproval. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section A.3 | Description :By December 31, 2010, the Borrower shall establish andthereafter maintain an adequate monitoring and evaluation system designed tomonitor progress achieved in the execution of theProject. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section B | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that the Project is carried outin accordance with the provisions of the Anti-Corruption Guidelines. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.1 (i) | Description :The Borrower shall: (i) cause the Project to becarried out in conformity with the provisions of the SDR, the FDESP and the RPF; | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.1 (ii) | Description :(ii) inform the Bank of any developments in theEnvironmental Legislation applicable to, and that may affect the implementation of the Project; | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.1 (iii) | Description :and (iii) not change, modify or otherwise amendsaid SDR, FDESP and RPF in a manner inconsistent with the Project, without prior concurrence of the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.2 (i) | Description :The Borrower shall cause MAWRF to ensure that: (i)prior to carrying out any Project activities not identified, assessed, nor included in the FDESP, such activities shall be subjectto an EA; | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.2 (ii) | Description :and (ii) mitigating and monitoring measures forimpacts of said activities are carried out in accordance with the provisions of theSDR and the FDESP. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.3 | Description :The Borrower shall cause to be prepared and provided tothe Bank for its review reports on the application of the provisions of theFDESP to Project activities. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section C.4 | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that any activity under Part Aand Part B.2 of the Project, requiring land acquisition is carried out in accordance with the RPF. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section II A | Description :Each Project Report shall cover the period of onecalendar semester, and shall be furnished to the Bank not later than forty five (45) days after the end of the period covered bysuch report. | Frequency :Yearly
